        718.2289428710938,
        486.1000061035156,
        728.7889404296875
      ],
      "max_font_size": 10.5600004196167,
      "text": "不全及心房颤动时N 末端前体脑钠肽（NT-proBNP）＞332ng/L；",
      "is_heading": false
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
